<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:36:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报道：国防部长加兰特告诉人质家属“以色列有史以来最接近达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</link><description>据以色列第 12 频道援引未透露姓名的消息人士的报道，10 月 7 日，国防部长约阿夫·加兰特在会见在军事基地被绑架的以色列国防军女观察员家属时，暗示与哈马斯的人质谈判取得了重大进展</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家解释为什么斯德泰曼拘留设施不依法运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</link><description>该国表示打算将被拘留者转移到以色列其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟。在该州再次要求推迟后，法官要求政府在 10 天内做出回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，以色列与哈马斯开战。十年后，我们正经历着残酷的重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</link><description>我们已经用十年的时间从​​ 2014 年发生的事件中汲取教训，其中许多事件似乎预示着即将发生的事情。这一次，没有任何借口让加沙恢复现状——我们已经看到，这对于以色列人和巴勒斯坦人来说是多么不可持续和危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称，试图杀死德伊夫损害了与哈马斯的停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</link><description>一位以色列消息人士表示，“事情并没有像往常一样进行。”一位政府消息人士称，“哈马斯遭受了严重打击，他们对这一事件的反应非常软弱，近乎无反应。”结果，摩萨德主任尚未启程前往卡塔尔进行谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯人和巴勒斯坦人谴责以色列对“安全”区哈马斯指挥官的不作为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</link><description>在以色列对本应安全的地区进行大规模轰炸后，以色列阿拉伯城市的抗议者集会“声援加沙人民”，而整个阿拉伯世界的许多人则在社交媒体上指责他们的政府缺乏保护。结束战争的努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟制裁以色列极右翼领导人、极端主义定居者团体和前哨基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</link><description>以色列担心，在国际法院就以色列占领西岸是否符合国际法的合法性作出裁决后，对与西岸定居点有关的实体和个人实施的日益严厉的制裁将会加剧</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</guid></item><item><title>报告：与叙利亚阿萨德有联系的商人在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</link><description>据报道，与真主党有经济联系、此前曾受到美国制裁的巴拉·卡特吉(Baraa Katerji)在袭击中身亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战，第 283 天：以色列国防军袭击加沙中部南部；欧盟制裁以色列极右活动人士和实体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</link><description>在哈马斯发表相互矛盾的声明后，以色列官员表示，达成协议的谈判仍在继续。 ■ 以色列国防军袭击加沙南部和中部，试图对哈马斯施加更大压力。 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡就煽动反对他的问题举行会议后，反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示：“内塔尼亚胡不是一个受害者;他是个爱发牢骚的人，也是个胆小鬼。 ■ 欧盟对五名以色列极右活动分子和三个实体实施制裁 ■ 战争进入 283 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡在人质交易关键时刻批评卡塔尔后引发新争议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</link><description>据瓦拉报道，他在迈阿密举行的一次会议上表示，卡塔尔是“仅次于伊朗的世界第二大恐怖主义资助者”，并声称他们资助反以色列校园抗议活动。一名卡塔尔官员驳斥了这些说法，称其为“无稽之谈”，并表示这可能会使人质谈判“复杂化”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</guid></item><item><title>Wiz 做什么？谷歌将如何从此次收购中受益？这对以色列意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</link><description>如果这家以色列网络安全公司确实被美国科技巨头以 230 亿美元收购，这将标志着以色列经济的一个里程碑。它的创始人和员工会赚多少钱，它将如何影响云计算，以及以色列将从销售中获得多少税收？</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</guid></item><item><title>“无犹太复国主义区”：全球旅游景点越来越不受欢迎以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/zionist-free-zone-israelis-are-increasingly-unwanted-at-global-tourism-sites/00000190-b60f-d9f4-afd5-fe8fec740000</link><description>从京都的一家酒店到爱丁堡的三明治店，全世界都对以色列人产生敌意，他们了解到假期并不能保护他们免受加沙战争的影响</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/zionist-free-zone-israelis-are-increasingly-unwanted-at-global-tourism-sites/00000190-b60f-d9f4-afd5-fe8fec740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须允许记者进入加沙自由独立报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-allow-journalists-into-gaza-to-report-freely-and-independently/00000190-b1b6-d3c7-ab94-bfff13050000</link><description>包括《纽约时报》、BBC 和 CNN 在内的 70 多个新闻和民间社会组织签署了一封致以色列的公开信，重申呼吁国际媒体不受限制地进入加沙。持续的限制导致错误信息和虚假信息泛滥</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-allow-journalists-into-gaza-to-report-freely-and-independently/00000190-b1b6-d3c7-ab94-bfff13050000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境社区谴责最高安全顾问内塔尼亚胡在 10 月 7 日之后未能访问基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-blasts-netanyahu-top-security-adviser-for-failing-to-visit-community-after-oct-7/00000190-b610-df08-a9fe-f7d0f07a0000</link><description>尼尔奥兹集体农场（Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz）是哈马斯袭击中受灾最严重的社区之一，在国家安全负责人为总理辩护“将一生奉献给加沙边境社区的重建”后，该组织的成员对他进行了猛烈反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:17:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-blasts-netanyahu-top-security-adviser-for-failing-to-visit-community-after-oct-7/00000190-b610-df08-a9fe-f7d0f07a0000</guid></item><item><title>阿莫斯·哈雷尔：“内塔尼亚胡正在利用特朗普枪击事件来诽谤以色列的抗议运动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-15/ty-article-podcast/amos-harel-netanyahu-is-using-the-trump-shooting-to-vilify-israels-protest-movement/00000190-b59a-df08-a9fe-f5dae7f80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-15/ty-article-podcast/amos-harel-netanyahu-is-using-the-trump-shooting-to-vilify-israels-protest-movement/00000190-b59a-df08-a9fe-f5dae7f80000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼极端分子袭击组织者后，耶路撒冷警方拆除了艺术展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-police-takes-down-art-exhibit-after-far-right-extremists-assault-organizers/00000190-b5d3-df08-a9fe-f5d3c4310000</link><description>该展览试图强调自 10 月 7 日以来冲突对儿童的影响。极右极端分子指责组织者“反对以色列国防军士兵”，其中一人破坏了艺术品并袭击了一名组织者</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-police-takes-down-art-exhibit-after-far-right-extremists-assault-organizers/00000190-b5d3-df08-a9fe-f5d3c4310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等教育机构将讨论扩大性别隔离研究，反对最高法院裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/education-council-to-discuss-expanding-gender-segregated-studies-against-top-court-ruling/00000190-b599-db94-a7fa-ffdfb3e60000</link><description>目前的大纲只允许本科生班级实行性别隔离。 2021年，高等法院裁定不应扩大范围以包括研究生课程</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:43:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/education-council-to-discuss-expanding-gender-segregated-studies-against-top-court-ruling/00000190-b599-db94-a7fa-ffdfb3e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高警察在告别演说中警告称，为防止警察介入政治，“日常斗争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-farewell-speech-top-cop-warns-of-daily-battles-to-keep-politics-out-of-police/00000190-b557-d96f-a1f6-ff5f277d0000</link><description>科比·沙卜泰在退休活动上表示，他作为专员的任期“与试图“影响和引导”警方的政客关系非常紧张。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本格维尔没有受到邀请，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡也没有出席</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-farewell-speech-top-cop-warns-of-daily-battles-to-keep-politics-out-of-police/00000190-b557-d96f-a1f6-ff5f277d0000</guid></item><item><title>来自欧洲各地的犹太青年写下他们的生活。现在和85年前</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jewish-youth-from-around-europe-write-about-their-lives-now-and-85-years-ago/00000190-a26f-da1a-adf0-a6ff4cb40000</link><description>万花筒项目复兴了一项因大屠杀而中断的倡议：为来自欧洲各地的犹太青年举办自传写作比赛</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:31:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jewish-youth-from-around-europe-write-about-their-lives-now-and-85-years-ago/00000190-a26f-da1a-adf0-a6ff4cb40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的发牢骚戏剧利用特朗普的暗杀企图来削减以色列总检察长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-petulant-theatrics-leverage-trump-assassination-attempt-to-axe-israels-ag/00000190-b537-df08-a9fe-f5f7f92d0000</link><description>人质？伤亡？战争？以色列内阁用了两个小时的时间讨论了总理的悲惨命运，总理利用受害者的叙述并推动解雇目中无人的总检察长</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 08:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-petulant-theatrics-leverage-trump-assassination-attempt-to-axe-israels-ag/00000190-b537-df08-a9fe-f5f7f92d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙的暗杀行动是否终止了人质交易？答案就在卡塔尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/did-israels-assassination-attempt-kill-the-hostage-deal-the-answer-is-in-qatar/00000190-b2e1-d9c3-ad99-bfe351500000</link><description>以色列官员认为，在加沙刺杀哈马斯二号人物的企图将有助于谈判，但有人担心辛瓦尔将继续存在，甚至以他的生命为代价；暗杀企图失败后，特朗普的预期激增可能给内塔尼亚胡带来两个不同的挑战</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 03:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/did-israels-assassination-attempt-kill-the-hostage-deal-the-answer-is-in-qatar/00000190-b2e1-d9c3-ad99-bfe351500000</guid></item></channel></rss>